===Noun===

'''funicular'''

#A particular type of [[rail]] [[transit]] system which ascends a steep urban or mountain incline, having usually two [[car]]s sharing a single [[track]], with the cars linked by a [[cable]] and an arrangement of [[pulley]]s such that the descending car assists in the hoisting of the ascending car, i.e. the two cars serve as [[counterweight]]s for each other.

